provides state-based and date-based provisioning/deprovisioning capability.

VERSION - Static variable in class org.idmunit.Constants
IdMUnit versions should always directly correspond to the major release versions of Designer for Novell Identity Manager in order to be clear on which releases of IdMUnit have been certified for use with which versions of Designer.
